Q.  Alexander, could you talk about the feelings that were going through you when you heard your name called?
 
ALEXANDER SVITOV: It's real difficult to translate what feelings I have when I heard my name called.  Well, it looks like that I felt myself couldn't hear that last part.  
 

Q.  How much do you know about the Tampa Bay Lightning and what kind of players they have?
 
